    "created_at": "2015-07-01T15:50:54Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-01T15:50:54Z",
    "body": "This solves the issue:\n\n```\nsetInterval(function(){\n        mainWindow.setAlwaysOnTop(true);\n    }, 1);\n```\n\nBut shouldn't have to do this... and I'm sure it has performance issues.\n"
