    "updated_at": "2015-07-07T03:47:45Z",
    "body": "We've definitely been hearing this happen with even non-topmost windows (i.e. topmost windows getting covered by Visual Studio or Excel). Could it be that if you `hide` a window and show it again, we forget to reset topmost flag?\n"
