    "updated_at": "2016-10-13T05:47:53Z",
    "body": "I had to periodically set my window always on top even in C# app.\n\nBut remember peeps, if you do interval make the time something reasonable like, `setInterval(function(){ mainWindow.setAlwaysOnTop(true);}, 10000);` 10 seconds... It does not go to wrong order very often.\n"
